workzen.xgen.type
Class XGenType

java.lang.Object
  workzen.xgen.type.XGenType
Direct Known Subclasses:
Blob, Boolean, Byte, Clob, Date, Decimal, Double, Float, Integer, Long, Short, Str, Time, Timestamp
public abstract class XGenType
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to map the "type" of an xgen field to an actual java type. It returns string values for the: Java classname, classname abbreviation, primitive type name, and the class primitive function that returns the primitive value. http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.3/docs/guide/jdbc/spec/jdbc-spec.frame8.html
